snippet.title: HOW BOTS SIGN Change Petitions & Fake Movements/Astroturfing - Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
Explains HOW Bots Sign Change Petitions and Social BOTS. Rotating IP, Shuffle IP, Gmails, multiple devices... for a PRICE to Fake Movements. Uses India IPs... How To.
My bot does over 100 in this SHORT video. I show IPv6 cheaply made, NO recaptcha slowing it down. APIs are NOT needed. 10-20 VPSes can do the 20,000 signatures a day.

Sharing petition makes Change.org think it's 'real people'
As you can see, the profiles are faceless when sharing.
Get to 1.8 million signatures like on Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2
Or 500,000 on Johnny Depp petitions with 146 comments.

What is Astroturfing? What are Social Bots?
They search social networks for discussions on pre-defined topics (data evaluation just like web crawlers) and influences them as a virtual conversation participant (simulation of conversations like a chat bot).
https://www.ionos.com/digitalguide/online-marketing/social-media/social-bots/
